Class ProcessPanel

    public class ProcessPanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements IProcessServiceListener
    A panel to display processing information. Listens to the process service to update a JTextArea field with the appropriate output from the service.
    Author:
    Lucas Carpenter
